snippet: Abid Naseer, who was arrested in Britain in 2009, is accused of being part of a cell of Al Qaeda.
abstract: Abid Naseer, Pakistani man who was arrested in Britain in 2009 for plotting terrorist attacks there and in the United States, is extradited to face charges in New York; Naseer is accused of being part of a cell of Al Qaeda.
lead_paragraph: Abid Naseer, who was arrested in Britain in 2009, is accused of being part of a cell of Al Qaeda.

headline.seo: Abid Naseer Extradited to New York From Britain on Terror Charges
headline.main: Pakistani in Terror Case Is Extradited to New York
